data.description: Enjoy this WATERFRONT home on NAVIGABLE 80 miles of lakes/canals from Palm Beach to Boca! New Tile Roof, Impact Windows, Plantation shutters to help maintain energy efficiency. A true 3 bed, 2.5 bath plus loft for multiple use. Beautiful wood tile downstairs, carpet upstairs, freshly painted interior, new water heater, new dishwasher, stainless appliance package, well maintained HVAC system, and a spacious floorplan with soaring ceiling for lots of natural light. Kitchen with nook to enjoy the view out the picture window. 2 patios, one is screened and one for entertaining. Master with walk in closet. Plenty of closet space throughout home. Secluded community  with 2 pools, 1 across the street! 4 miles to the beach. Home can be a tranquil setting or ready to enjoy the S. Florida lifestyle!
